/* Author : Masango Promise
   Name   : fb2bmp.c (Framebuffer-to-bitmap)
   Description: Take a screenshot of the current window and save it as a windows bitmap image (24-bit).
*/

/* info */
Originally written to be ran on a 32-bit machine (Android) but is should work with most systems.
Compile using the android C cross-compiler arm-linux-androideabi-gcc.
